# Privacy Policy — Sudoku (com.rnr.sudokunoads)

_Last updated: 06/07/2026

## English

This app was built to respect your privacy. In short: **it collects nothing about you.**

**No data collection.** The app does not collect, transmit, or share any personal information. There are no accounts, no logins, and no sign-up.

**No tracking or analytics.** The app contains no advertising SDKs, no analytics tools, and no third-party trackers.

**Local storage only.** Your game progress, statistics, streaks, and settings are stored **only on your device**, so you can resume where you left off. This information never leaves your phone and is not accessible to us or anyone else. Uninstalling the app removes it.

**No special permissions.** The app does not request access to your location, contacts, camera, microphone, files, or any other sensitive data. It works fully offline.

**Children.** Because the app collects no data from anyone, it collects no data from children either.

**In-app purchases (if offered).** If the app ever offers optional purchases (such as a supporter option or tips), those payments are processed entirely by Google Play. We never receive or store your payment details.

**Changes.** If this policy changes, the updated version will be posted at this same address, with a new date above.

**Contact.** Questions? Reach out at: inveniapps@gmail.com — or on X: @InveniApps

